<paragraph id="2FEC8088EE2DB0A93CD9900BAD0CCDC7" pageNumber="755">color Major: head, appendages, and most of gaster light reddish yellow (light &quot;orange&quot;); mesosoma, waist, and part of gaster medium reddish yellow (medium &quot;orange&quot;).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
